Q9. Display vid, vname, price,details and total price for each vehicle.
       total price = price - discount


mysql> SELECT vid, vname, price, details, price-(price* (discount/100)) "Total price" FROM vehicle;
+------+---------------+--------+------------------------+-------------+
| vid  | vname         | price  | details                | Total price |
+------+---------------+--------+------------------------+-------------+
|    1 | activa        |  80000 | Two wheeler. Sturd     |       72000 |
|    2 | Santro        |  95000 | Product of Hyandai.    |       76000 |
|    3 | Yamaha        | 160000 | Sturdy and good milage |      152000 |
|    4 | I10           | 300000 | Good small car         |      276000 |
|    5 | WaganR        | 250000 | Good milage car        |      225000 |
|    6 | hero splendor |  75000 | Best bike              |       68250 |
|    7 | Royal enfild  | 190000 | Royal Bike             |      180500 |
+------+---------------+--------+------------------------+-------------+
7 rows in set (0.00 sec)




